r_stories/img_kv_member-stories_pc.png\">\n                        <source media=\"(max-width:768px)\"\n                            srcset=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/member_stories/img_kv_member-stories_sp.png\">\n                        <img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/member_stories/img_kv_member-stories_pc.png\" alt=\"\">\n                    </picture>\n                    <div class=\"page-title\">\n                        <h1><span class=\"font-quattro bold\">MEMBER STORIES</span><small>社員インタビュー</small></h1>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n\n        <section class=\"member-stories-index\">\n    <div class=\"l-inner\">\n      <ul class=\"index-list\">\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"nishida/\">\n            <div class=\"thumb\"><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/member_stories/img_index_01.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <h2><span>ドキュメンタリー最高賞受賞！仕事嫌いな若手ディレクターを支えた「元作り手」エージェントの影の奮闘</span></h2>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"takeuchi/\">\n            <div class=\"thumb\"><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/member_stories/img_index_02.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <h2><span>最悪の状況から逃げない！周囲を巻き込みTV不況の最中ながら信頼を得た、ある女性エージェントの話</span></h2>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <!-- li>\n          <a href=\"ishii/\">\n            <div class=\"thumb\"><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/member_stories/img_index_03.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <h2><span>崖っぷちスタート！ソフトウェア開発を行う某大企業で伝説となった、あるエージェントの1ヵ月の奇跡</span></h2>\n          </a>\n        </li -->\n        <li>\n          <a href=\"kaneda/\">\n            <div class=\"thumb\"><img src=\"/mt-static/support/theme_static/recruit/images/member_stories/img_index_04.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n            <h2><span>重版8万部！マイナーコンテンツ「指ヨガ」を一大ムーブメントに仕立てた業界ド素人の無謀な挑戦</span></h2>\n          </a>\n        </li>\n        <li>\n          <a href=